# CODEOWNERS — the harness's immutable control plane (HG-0002)
# =============================================================================
# These paths are the controls that constrain the autonomous build agent: its
# rules, gates, hooks, reviewers, CI, governance, and the spec/ADR canon. Per
# HG-0002, a change to any of them is a *control change* and must be approved by
# a human group the build agent is NOT a member of — separate from ordinary
# feature-work review (HG-0001).
#
# WHY A SANDBOX ISN'T ENOUGH: running the agent only in isolated, ephemeral
# sandboxes does not make these controls tamper-proof — a sandboxed agent can
# still edit its own skills/hooks/gates in the repo it is working on. Immutability
# has to be enforced HERE, in the GitHub control surface, outside the agent's
# write scope. This file is that enforcement (once activated — see SETUP).
#
# SETUP — the bank-config step; this file is INERT until all three are done:
#   1. Create the two GitHub teams below with accountable HUMANS. The build
#      agent / bot identity MUST NOT be a member of either team and must not be
#      able to approve its own PRs.
#        @openfinance-os/ofbo-maintainers       — baseline human reviewers
#        @openfinance-os/control-plane-owners    — control-plane change approvers
#   2. Settings → Branches → protect `main`: enable "Require review from Code
#      Owners", "Dismiss stale approvals", and "Do not allow bypass". Without
#      this, CODEOWNERS is advisory only (HG-0001/HG-0002 are not enforced).
#   3. Make the Q1–Q4.5 + discovery/waist checks REQUIRED status checks.
#
# (The team handles are PLACEHOLDERS. Until the teams exist GitHub will flag them
#  as unknown owners and the rules won't bind — which is why this file is safe to
#  merge ahead of the org setup. Substitute the bank's real team slugs.)
#
# Syntax: last matching pattern wins, so the catch-all is FIRST and the stricter
# control-plane patterns come AFTER it.
# =============================================================================

# --- Baseline: every change needs a human reviewer (HG-0001) ---
*                           @openfinance-os/ofbo-maintainers

# --- Control plane (HG-0002): the agent's own guardrails — stricter owners ---
/.github/                   @openfinance-os/control-plane-owners
/.github/workflows/         @openfinance-os/control-plane-owners
/.github/CODEOWNERS         @openfinance-os/control-plane-owners
/.claude/                   @openfinance-os/control-plane-owners
/CLAUDE.md                  @openfinance-os/control-plane-owners
/scripts/                   @openfinance-os/control-plane-owners
/docs/governance/           @openfinance-os/control-plane-owners

# --- Canon of record: contract + architecture decisions (human-only already) ---
/specs/                     @openfinance-os/control-plane-owners
/docs/adrs/                 @openfinance-os/control-plane-owners
